  "description": "v4 4-die 2.5D interposer benchmark with per-die BIST engines. Dies are side-by-side on a silicon interposer (layer_index=0 for all), connected by interposer links. FPP is only on die0 and die2 -- die1 and die3 use serial TAP only, reflecting that FPP is optional (IEEE 1838 Clause 7) and not every die gets it.",
